author: Source: Daily Herald
title: Mona Barthel to face Misaki Doi in Luxembourg Open final - Daily Herald
text:
Misaki Doi will take on Mona Barthel in her first WTA tour final after Alison Van Uytvanck was forced to retire when trailing 6-4 against the Japanese player in their semifinal at the Luxembourg Open on Saturday. Van Uytvanck, a quarterfinalist at the French Open, cited a viral illness.
 Daily Herald.
